The Text widget in Flutter is used to display a string of text (words, sentences, numbers) on the screen.
It is one of the most basic and commonly used widgets in Flutter UI development.
You can style text using properties like font size, color, font weight, alignment, letter spacing, decoration, etc.

Marathi:
Flutter ‡§Æ‡§ß‡•Ä‡§≤ Text widget ‡§π‡•á ‡§∏‡•ç‡§ï‡•ç‡§∞‡•Ä‡§®‡§µ‡§∞ ‡§Æ‡§ú‡§ï‡•Ç‡§∞ (text) ‡§¶‡§æ‡§ñ‡§µ‡§£‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ‡§∏‡§æ‡§†‡•Ä ‡§µ‡§æ‡§™‡§∞‡§≤‡•á ‡§ú‡§æ‡§§‡•á.
‡§π‡•á Flutter ‡§Æ‡§ß‡•Ä‡§≤ ‡§∏‡§∞‡•ç‡§µ‡§æ‡§§ ‡§Æ‡§π‡§§‡•ç‡§§‡•ç‡§µ‡§æ‡§ö‡•á ‡§Ü‡§£‡§ø ‡§Æ‡•Ç‡§≤‡§≠‡•Ç‡§§ widget ‡§Ü‡§π‡•á.
‡§Ø‡§æ‡§§ ‡§Ü‡§™‡§£ font size, color, weight, alignment, spacing, decoration ‡§á‡§§‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ‡§¶‡•Ä ‡§ó‡•Å‡§£‡§ß‡§∞‡•ç‡§Æ ‡§µ‡§æ‡§™‡§∞‡•Ç‡§® ‡§Æ‡§ú‡§ï‡•Ç‡§∞ ‡§∏‡•Å‡§Ç‡§¶‡§∞‡§™‡§£‡•á ‡§¶‡§æ‡§ñ‡§µ‡•Ç ‡§∂‡§ï‡§§‡•ã.

Text(
  'Hello Flutter!',
)


import 'package:flutter/material.dart';

void main() {
  runApp(MaterialApp(
    home: Scaffold(
      appBar: AppBar(title: Text("Text Widget Example")),
      body: Center(
        child: Text(
          'Welcome to Flutter!',
          style: TextStyle(
            fontSize: 24,
            color: Colors.blue,
            fontWeight: FontWeight.bold,
            letterSpacing: 2,
            wordSpacing: 5,
            fontStyle: FontStyle.italic,
            decoration: TextDecoration.underline,
          ),
          textAlign: TextAlign.center,
        ),
      ),
    ),
  ));
}

üìò Explanation of Properties (‡§ó‡•Å‡§£‡§ß‡§∞‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ‡§Ç‡§ö‡•á ‡§∏‡•ç‡§™‡§∑‡•ç‡§ü‡•Ä‡§ï‡§∞‡§£)
Property	Description (English)	‡§∏‡•ç‡§™‡§∑‡•ç‡§ü‡•Ä‡§ï‡§∞‡§£ (Marathi)
data	The text string to display.	‡§¶‡§æ‡§ñ‡§µ‡§æ‡§Ø‡§ö‡§æ ‡§Æ‡§ú‡§ï‡•Ç‡§∞.
style	Defines font, color, weight, size, spacing, etc.	‡§´‡•â‡§®‡•ç‡§ü, ‡§∞‡§Ç‡§ó, ‡§Ü‡§ï‡§æ‡§∞, ‡§µ‡§ú‡§®, ‡§Ö‡§Ç‡§§‡§∞ ‡§á‡§§‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ‡§¶‡•Ä ‡§†‡§∞‡§µ‡§§‡•á.
textAlign	Aligns text: left, right, center, justify.	‡§Æ‡§ú‡§ï‡•Ç‡§∞ ‡§ï‡•Å‡§†‡•á ‡§†‡•á‡§µ‡§æ‡§Ø‡§ö‡§æ: ‡§°‡§æ‡§µ‡•Ä‡§ï‡§°‡•á, ‡§â‡§ú‡§µ‡•Ä‡§ï‡§°‡•á, ‡§Æ‡§ß‡•ç‡§Ø‡§≠‡§æ‡§ó‡•Ä ‡§ï‡§ø‡§Ç‡§µ‡§æ ‡§™‡•Ç‡§∞‡•ç‡§£ ‡§™‡§∏‡§∞‡§µ‡•Ç‡§®.
maxLines	Limits number of lines shown.	‡§ï‡§ø‡§§‡•Ä ‡§ì‡§≥‡•Ä‡§™‡§∞‡•ç‡§Ø‡§Ç‡§§ ‡§Æ‡§ú‡§ï‡•Ç‡§∞ ‡§¶‡§ø‡§∏‡§æ‡§µ‡§æ ‡§π‡•á ‡§†‡§∞‡§µ‡§§‡•á.
overflow	Handles overflow text (e.g. ellipsis ‚Äú...‚Äù).	‡§Æ‡§ú‡§ï‡•Ç‡§∞ ‡§ú‡§æ‡§∏‡•ç‡§§ ‡§ù‡§æ‡§≤‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ‡§∏ ‡§ï‡§∏‡§æ ‡§¶‡§æ‡§ñ‡§µ‡§æ‡§Ø‡§ö‡§æ (‡§â‡§¶‡§æ. ...).
softWrap	Breaks text into next line when needed.	‡§ó‡§∞‡§ú ‡§Ö‡§∏‡•á‡§≤ ‡§§‡•á‡§µ‡•ç‡§π‡§æ ‡§Æ‡§ú‡§ï‡•Ç‡§∞ ‡§™‡•Å‡§¢‡§ö‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ ‡§ì‡§≥‡•Ä‡§§ ‡§®‡•á‡§§‡•ã.
textDirection	Sets direction (ltr or rtl).	‡§Æ‡§ú‡§ï‡•Ç‡§∞‡§æ‡§ö‡§æ ‡§¶‡§ø‡§∂‡§æ (‡§°‡§æ‡§µ‡•Ä‡§ï‡§°‡•Ç‡§® ‡§â‡§ú‡§µ‡•Ä‡§ï‡§°‡•á ‡§ï‡§ø‡§Ç‡§µ‡§æ ‡§â‡§≤‡§ü).


‚ú® TextStyle Properties (Text ‡§∏‡§ú‡§µ‡§£‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ‡§∏‡§æ‡§†‡•Ä ‡§µ‡§æ‡§™‡§∞‡§≤‡•á ‡§ú‡§æ‡§£‡§æ‡§∞‡•á ‡§ó‡•Å‡§£‡§ß‡§∞‡•ç‡§Æ)
Property	English Meaning	Marathi ‡§Ö‡§∞‡•ç‡§•
color	Text color	‡§Æ‡§ú‡§ï‡•Ç‡§∞‡§æ‡§ö‡§æ ‡§∞‡§Ç‡§ó
fontSize	Size of the text	‡§Æ‡§ú‡§ï‡•Ç‡§∞‡§æ‡§ö‡§æ ‡§Ü‡§ï‡§æ‡§∞
fontWeight	Boldness (e.g. FontWeight.bold)	‡§ú‡§æ‡§°‡•Ä (‡§â‡§¶‡§æ. ‡§†‡§≥‡§ï ‡§Æ‡§ú‡§ï‡•Ç‡§∞)
fontStyle	Italic or normal	‡§§‡§ø‡§∞‡§™‡§æ ‡§ï‡§ø‡§Ç‡§µ‡§æ ‡§∏‡§∞‡§≥ ‡§Æ‡§ú‡§ï‡•Ç‡§∞
letterSpacing	Space between letters	‡§Ö‡§ï‡•ç‡§∑‡§∞‡§æ‡§Ç‡§Æ‡§ß‡•Ä‡§≤ ‡§Ö‡§Ç‡§§‡§∞
wordSpacing	Space between words	‡§∂‡§¨‡•ç‡§¶‡§æ‡§Ç‡§Æ‡§ß‡•Ä‡§≤ ‡§Ö‡§Ç‡§§‡§∞
decoration	Underline, overline, lineThrough	‡§∞‡•á‡§∑‡§æ (‡§ñ‡§æ‡§≤‡•Ä, ‡§µ‡§∞, ‡§Æ‡§ß‡•Ç‡§®)
backgroundColor	Background color of text	‡§Æ‡§ú‡§ï‡•Ç‡§∞‡§æ‡§ö‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ ‡§Æ‡§æ‡§ó‡•á ‡§∞‡§Ç‡§ó

üß† Example with Multiple Lines:
Text(
  'Flutter makes app development fast and easy.\nLearn once, build anywhere!',
  style: TextStyle(fontSize: 18, color: Colors.green),
  textAlign: TextAlign.center,
  maxLines: 2,
  overflow: TextOverflow.ellipsis,
)
